{"tid":2077370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要走到邊境「找中国報仇」10名印度孩童公路長征","createTime":"2020-06-24T08:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T16:35:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ea94a57e3ee9ae5bedf1435661a49781a69d7c39","tid":2077370,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"中印軍隊15日在加勒萬河谷（Galwan Valley）發生暴力衝突，造成印度20名士兵死亡。消息傳出後，印度國內民眾反中的情緒日漸高漲，揚言抵制中國製產品。印度警察近日在路上發現一群孩子，詢問後才知道他們因為中印衝突，打算走到邊境找對方報仇。<br />\n<br />\n根據當地媒體《News18》報導，北方邦阿里格爾縣（Aligarh）警方看到10名小孩走在高速公路邊，馬上將人攔下來盤問，得知他們因為看到新聞群起激憤，相約一起走到中國邊境，找解放軍打架，「我們要幫中國好好上一課」，替死去的士兵們報仇。<br />\n<br />\n原因揭曉後，員警們對這群小孩的行為感到震驚，佩服他們的愛國精神，更讚賞他們對家園、國人的愛，但沒有任由他們繼續行走，在苦口婆心的勸說下，將10名小孩安全送回家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200624/1745583.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200624%2F1745583.htm&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=9e978226\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200624/1745583.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4IBu5G24nGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4IBu5G24nGk&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=2e65e171\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4IBu5G24nGk</a>"},{"pid":"bc95ad447530bfe5674097fa7be48a8f930f13c2","tid":2077370,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4778a384763d9e371ee4068d300bc93bb43e2c","tid":2077370,"uid":277339,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"等睇中國有樣學樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65156a7faffe2f6a2055360e7d1d79ad99fe6d9